---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Monir Saikat";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="gif">
    <img width="150" height="200" alt="Monir Saikat" src="/dev.png" />
  </div>
  <h1>Monir-Saikat</h1>
  <span class="badge">Software Designer(Developer)</span>
  <h2>About</h2>
  <p>
    Hello! I'm a passionate technologist with over four years of experience in
    software development. My journey in the tech world has been driven by a deep
    love for technology and an insatiable curiosity to explore and master new
    tools and frameworks.
  </p>
  <p>
    I specialize in a wide array of technologies including JavaScript, React,
    Laravel, PHP, jQuery, Node.js with Express, MySQL, MongoDB, and Next.js. My
    expertise also extends to eCommerce solutions and various modern
    technologies. I am constantly learning and adapting to the latest
    advancements to stay at the forefront of the industry.
  </p>
  <p>
    Beyond coding, I have a profound interest in software architecture and
    design systems. I believe that the foundation of great software lies in a
    well-thought-out architecture and robust design principles. My passion for
    these areas drives me to create scalable, efficient, and maintainable
    solutions.
  </p>
  <p>
    I am enthusiastic about collaborating with others, sharing knowledge, and
    contributing to innovative projects that push the boundaries of what's
    possible with technology. Let's build something amazing together!
  </p>

  <!-- <div class="center">
    <a href="/works/">
      <button class="btn">My portfolio</button>
    </a>
  </div> -->
  <h2>Skills</h2>
  <div class="skills center">
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="PHP"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/php/php-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Laravel"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/laravel/laravel-original.svg"
    />

    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="JavaScript"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="jQuery"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/jquery/jquery-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="React"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/react/react-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Next.js"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/nextjs/nextjs-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="MySQL"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/mysql/mysql-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Node.js"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/nodejs/nodejs-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Express"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/express/express-original.svg"
    />
  </div>

  <h2>Interests</h2>
  <p>
    I am deeply passionate about technology and its endless possibilities. My
    interests span across various domains including software development with
    JavaScript, React, Laravel, and Node.js, as well as designing robust and
    scalable software architectures. I am particularly fascinated by modern web
    technologies and enjoy staying updated with the latest trends and tools to
    enhance my development skills. My enthusiasm extends to creating cohesive
    design systems and optimizing databases like MySQL and MongoDB.
    Additionally, I find joy in developing intuitive e-commerce solutions.
    Continuous learning and exploring new advancements in technology are
    integral to my personal and professional growth.
  </p>
</Layout>
